,Recommended,301120,25433046,"Posted: 9 September, 2016",all,Erect Tent,"This may be on sale for $5, but it is definitely worth the regular price of $20!Eastside Hockey Manager is an in-depth hockey team management game. It easily takes the cake over other titles, such as the NHL Be A GM Series and the Franchise Hockey Manager series. It's simulation aspect is what makes it far better than it's competition. The game will give you every stat, of every game, of every season. You can even coach the games live and be amazed at how realistic it really is. Determining who is on your roster, who plays, and what line they play on is all your choice. You can assign specific tactics for the whole team, a specific line, or even a specific player. The game gives you full control over the tactics, and management of a team. You may be overwhelmed at first, but you will get the hang of it eventually. The head coach can do the tactics for you, if you wish to focus on managing the team as a main priority.If you're a hockey fan, this game would be very fun for you. If you are coming from the Football Manager games, the same would apply. Eastside Hockey Manager gives you lots of enjoyment. Watching your young players develop will enlighten you. The game keeps track of all players' histories, showing stats from the start of the player's career. It gives you all resources needed to make a decision about your team.As the game is not liscensed by the NHL, the developer was not able to include real players, of any league.. However, we have an amazing community. We have created up-to-date rosters of all current world leagues, with accurate attributes pertaining to all the players. We have also created multiple online 30-player NHL leagues, which is similar to GMing in the actual NHL! Instead of manipulating the singleplayer AI GMs, you have to persuade other, live people. It truly never gets old. You can replay this game countless times. You will never get bored.All in all, Eastside Hockey 